  "title": "Operations & Dormitory Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Dormitory Management:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Operations:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain and update operational records and reports.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate daily operational tasks and follow up with relevant teams.</li>\n  <li>Assist in scheduling, logistics, and procurement activities.</li>\n  <li>Prepare reports and documentation for management.</li>\n  <li>Support general administrative tasks to ensure smooth operations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Operations &amp; Administrative Support:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain and update operational records, databases, and reports.</li>\n  <li>Assist in scheduling and coordinating operational activities across departments.</li>\n  <li>Support logistics, and inventory management where applicable.</li>\n  <li>Handle correspondence, documentation, and administrative tasks to support smooth workflow.</li>\n</ul>",
